              <a href="tel:4001234567">400-123-4567</a>
            </p>
            <p>地址：北京市朝阳区XXX街道XXX号</p>
          </div>
          <div class="footer-section">
            <h3>关注我们</h3>
            <div class="qr-code">
              <img src="/images/qrcode.png" alt="微信公众号二维码" onerror="this.style.display='none'">
              <p>扫码关注公众号</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-bottom">
          <p>&copy; 2024 企业名称. 保留所有权利.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>
    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
